---

<section id="projects">
  <hr class="neon-divider" />
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Transmissions</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">
      Creative <span class="accent-green">Explorations</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="proj-intro">
      Beyond the day job, these are the ideas I chase — studios, prototypes,
      and provocations at the edge of immersive technology.
      Navigate the file system below to explore.
    </p>

    <!-- Retro terminal file browser -->
    <div class="terminal-window">
      <!-- Title bar -->
      <div class="terminal-titlebar">
        <div class="titlebar-dots">
          <span class="dot dot--red"></span>
          <span class="dot dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="dot dot--green"></span>
        </div>
        <span class="titlebar-text" id="terminalTitle">sdyer@creative-lab:~/projects</span>
        <span class="titlebar-spacer"></span>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal body -->
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <!-- Loading state (shown until user scrolls here) -->
        <div class="terminal-loading" id="terminalLoading">
          <div class="loading-spinner" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <p class="loading-text">AWAITING CONNECTION<span class="loading-dots">...</span></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Crash overlay (triggered by corrupted file) -->
        <div class="crash-overlay hidden" id="crashOverlay">
          <div class="crash-content">
            <p class="crash-header">☠ FATAL EXCEPTION ☠</p>
            <p class="crash-code">ERROR 0x00000404 — FILE_NOT_FOUND_BUT_ALSO_CURSED</p>
            <div class="crash-body">
              <p>> Attempted to open: AI_Agriculture.exe</p>
              <p>> File integrity check: <span class="crash-red">FAILED</span></p>
              <p>> Reason: This project doesn't exist yet lol</p>
              <p>> Vibes: <span class="crash-red">SUSPICIOUS</span></p>
              <p>&nbsp;</p>
              <p>> Recovering system...</p>
              <p>> Quarantining file...</p>
              <p class="crash-blink">DO NOT CLICK SUSPICIOUS FILES ▌</p>
            </div>
            <div class="crash-progress">
              <div class="crash-progress-bar" id="crashProgressBar"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="crash-status" id="crashStatus">REBOOTING IN 3...</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Boot sequence area (typed in by JS) -->
        <div class="terminal-boot hidden" id="terminalBoot"></div>

        <!-- Main content (hidden until boot completes) -->
        <div class="terminal-main hidden" id="terminalMain">
          <!-- Breadcrumb path -->
          <div class="terminal-path" id="terminalPath">
            <span class="path-segment path-root" data-nav="root">~/projects</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Root directory listing -->
          <div class="fs-view" id="viewRoot">
          <div class="terminal-output">
            <p class="cmd-line"><span class="prompt-green">sdyer@creative-lab</span>:<span class="prompt-cyan">~/projects</span>$ ls -la</p>
            <p class="cmd-output">total 5 entries</p>
            <p class="cmd-output dim">drwxr-xr-x  4 sdyer  staff  128 Mar 24 09:41 .</p>
            <p class="cmd-output dim">drwxr-xr-x  8 sdyer  staff  256 Mar 24 09:41 ..</p>
          </div>

          <div class="fs-listing">
            <button class="fs-item fs-folder" data-target="subSpatial">
              <span class="fs-icon">📁</span>
              <span class="fs-name">Sub_Spatial_Studio/</span>
              <span class="fs-meta">drwxr-xr-x · 2.4GB · ACTIVE</span>
              <span class="fs-arrow">→</span>
